title: How the World Is Messing With Investors and the Fed
text:
The world is messing with the Federal Reserve’s plans. Investors should be able to relate.
Fed Chairwoman Janet Yellen in a speech late Thursday said the central bank aims to raise rates later this year. In doing so, she made the case that despite last week’s decision to keep rates on hold, trouble overseas wasn’t likely to have a significant effect on future policy decisions.
